A whimsical, slightly hazy illustration of a lush, ancient forest intertwined with a warmly lit, Italian pizzeria – Argoth Pizza Place – complete with checkered tablecloths, overflowing pizza boxes, and a friendly, slightly inebriated gnome bartender pouring a sparkling, iridescent beverage, all set within a vibrant, otherworldly forest landscape, painterly style, magic the gathering card art.